### Chapter 6 — Finding Job Openings

- CSC portals, BARMM Official Gazette, Parliament website, social media
- Informal channels (word of mouth, networking — the reality)
- Scholarship-to-employment pipelines (AHME, ESKEY)
- Internship and OJT pathways
